text: Ravi Rajendra Maurya (born 18 November 1997) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Nagaland in the 2018–19 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 19 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Nagaland cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
